choices.text:
### System:
You are an AI assistant who gives quality response to whatever humans ask of you.

### Human:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for this week.  I can't have dairy, garlic, honey, almonds, pistachios, or cashews

### Assistant:

Day 1:
Breakfast - Vegan protein smoothie bowl with mixed berries and chia seeds.
Lunch - Quinoa salad with roasted vegetables (zucchini, eggplant, bell peppers) and avocado dressing.
Dinner - Baked tofu stir-fry with broccoli, mushrooms, snap peas, and brown rice.
